==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg-y|indemnit|y}}

# {{law}} an [[obligation]] or [[duty]] upon an individual to incurr the losses of another. 
# [[repayment]]
# {{law}} the right of an injured party to shift the loss onto the party responsible for the loss.

